                                                    <div class="gdlr-core-title-item-title-wrap clearfix">
                                                        <h3 class="gdlr-core-title-item-title gdlr-core-skin-title " id="h3_983a_4">General Fund</h3></div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="gdlr-core-pbf-element">
                                                <div class="gdlr-core-text-box-item gdlr-core-item-pdlr gdlr-core-item-pdb gdlr-core-left-align">
                                                    <div class="gdlr-core-text-box-item-content" id="div_983a_27">
                                                        <p>Giving to our general fund allows the school to allocate your gift to the area of greatest need. It could help the school renovate an existing classroom, provide financial assistance for a deserving child, or invest in a new technology.</p>
